{"tid":361332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再爆邊境衝突！中國士兵拿鐵棒石頭和印度互毆","createTime":"2017-08-16T05:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T05:48:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c52373f8d3c644a71c24fcaaf1166ca8504283","tid":361332,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:04:43.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國與印度軍隊在洞朗地區的邊界衝突已達2個月，原先傳出印度撤離大批人員，緊張局勢貌似緩解，但現在又傳出，雙方在另一處爭議地區發生爭吵，中方甚至帶著鐵棒和石頭和印度大打出手，兩邊皆有人受傷。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，印度新德里有消息指出，當地時間週二，印度士兵打算進入由印度北部的拉達克（Ladakh）地區時，遭到中國士兵阻止，該地區鄰近雙方仍有爭議的班公錯（Pangong lake）湖附近。<br />\n<br />\n中國士兵拿著鐵棒和石頭與印度大打出手，雙方皆有少部分人受傷。報導中指出，中印時常互控對方侵入邊界，但卻鮮有實際衝突發生。印度軍方和中國國防、外交部對此都尚無評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2164443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2164443&d=MmY%2BrEgLL5rawwX1UuTFPTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4da44927\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2164443&h=6884fcf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2164443</a>"},{"pid":"2372fa3b4f31c2fcfa0c5990c87529e320ae6568","tid":361332,"uid":189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"石器時代？"},{"pid":"40326845361359670830aafa7f33cef2505c975b","tid":361332,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:08:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共狗劉大導好應該即刻開套：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n古惑仔：支印大孽</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"49e7042cb134e7036a7f7fb9abfe426ea2529883","tid":361332,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/130857_f9f9f8c5ef356789fb3ca2e8ac54dc5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn